title: LvL 3 Profile
body:
It says that I am only level 3 when I Know that I am higher than that.

Sync plez

replies.body: Yup, your profile needs to sync to the boards when posting for the first time.  Glad everything is okay now!

Posting or using the [syncing tool](https://boards.na.leagueoflegends.com/en/c/help-support/fos1aFEB-boards-profile-syncing-tool) will update your level! You should be able to post where you wanted to now.
Sorry, when I was looking up my issue I didn't find this. Thanks!
